Uses of Package
sbmlme.converter

  • Packages that use sbmlme.converter 
    Package Description
    sbmlme.converter
    The SBMLme converter package contains method for a bidirectional converter between the JSON schema of a COBRAme model and its SBMLme representation.
  • Classes in sbmlme.converter used by sbmlme.converter 
    Class and Description
    MEJsonConstants
    Contains constants required for the conversion between the COBRAme JSON schema and SBMLme schema.
    MEJsonMetabolite
    Represents the JSON format of a species in a COBRAme model.
    MEJsonMetaboliteType
    Represents the species type in a COBRAme model.
    MEJsonMetaboliteTypeAttributes
    Represents attributes of different metabolite types in the COBRAme JSON schema.
    MEJsonProcessData
    Represents a process data object in a COBRAme JSON schema.
    MEJsonProcessDataType
    Represents the different types of process data in a COBRAme JSON schema.
    MEJsonProcessDataTypeAttributes
    Represents the attributes of process data objects in the COBRAme JSON schema.
    MEJsonReaction
    Represents the JSON schema of a single reaction entry in the list of reactions in a COBRAme JSON file.
    MEJsonReactionType
    Represents the different types of reactions in a COBRAme JSON schema.
    MEJsonReactionTypeAttributes
    Represents the JSON schema for the inner attributes of the different reaction types.
